Actually, I made this work:<p>1)  Inject JQuery as described on this website:  <a href="http://www.learningjquery.com/2009/04/better-stronger-safer-jquerify-bookmarklet" rel="nofollow">http://www.learningjquery.com/2009/04/better-stronger-safer-...</a><p>2)  Then open your JS console and copy and paste this in:<p>$("textarea").keyup(function(){
	    try {
        formatter.set(editor.get())
    } catch (a) {
        notify.showError(a)
    }
});<p>And viola!  It will change in real time from the left side to the right.  Doing the opposite should be trivial.<p>Enjoy.<p>PS:  This is a total hack obviously.  Not production stuff.
